961
02:28:52,680 --> 02:28:56,720
like the reflection of a town would be in a mirror,

962
02:28:56,920 --> 02:28:59,040
but which appears outside

963
02:28:59,240 --> 02:29:02,480
like a dream seen in a sleep.

964
02:29:02,720 --> 02:29:07,360
Salutation to Sakshat Shri Guru Dakshinamurti,

965
02:29:07,560 --> 02:29:10,480
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

966
02:29:10,720 --> 02:29:17,040
who like a mandarin or a maha yogi creates through her maya

967
02:29:17,280 --> 02:29:20,960
at her own free will this universe

968
02:29:21,160 --> 02:29:26,240
which was within her like a tree is in the seed.

969
02:29:26,440 --> 02:29:31,080
Salutation to Sakshat Shri Guru Dakshinamurti,

970
02:29:31,280 --> 02:29:33,680
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

971
02:29:33,880 --> 02:29:38,200
whose presence is felt as the pulsation everywhere

972
02:29:38,400 --> 02:29:41,000
in this illusöry universe,

973
02:29:41,200 --> 02:29:42,960
who gives enlightenment

974
02:29:43,160 --> 02:29:47,640
of "Thou Are That" to those who surrender

975
02:29:47,840 --> 02:29:52,040
and whose realization would obviate repeated birth

976
02:29:52,240 --> 02:29:55,040
in the ocean of illusion.

977
02:29:55,560 --> 02:30:00,400
Salutation to Sakshat Shri Guru Dakshinamurti,

978
02:30:00,600 --> 02:30:03,560
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

979
02:30:03,760 --> 02:30:08,480
whose knowledge pulsates from our own being

980
02:30:08,680 --> 02:30:13,280
like the light of a lamp being placed into a pitcher

981
02:30:13,480 --> 02:30:19,680
having numerous holes and thereby reveals the true nature

982
02:30:19,880 --> 02:30:23,360
of all that is there in the universe.

983
02:30:24,080 --> 02:30:28,320
Salutation to Sakshat Shri Guru Dakshinamurti,

984
02:30:28,520 --> 02:30:31,480
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

985
02:30:31,680 --> 02:30:36,240
who by Her Grace removes the ocean of illusion

986
02:30:36,440 --> 02:30:38,800
that has come into existence

987
02:30:39,000 --> 02:30:42,320
due to the imagination and play of Maya

988
02:30:42,520 --> 02:30:49,080
and because of which people go into the state of "branthi"

989
02:30:49,280 --> 02:30:52,160
and forget their spirit.

990
02:30:52,960 --> 02:30:57,280
Salutation to Sakshat Shri Guru Dakshinamurti,

991
02:30:57,480 --> 02:31:00,520
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

992
02:31:00,720 --> 02:31:07,320
by whose Grace one receives the realization of ones spirit

993
02:31:07,520 --> 02:31:12,120
which is until then overcast by Maya

994
02:31:12,320 --> 02:31:17,320
like the moon is overshadowed by the planet rahu.

995
02:31:18,120 --> 02:31:23,640
Salutation to Sakshat Shri Guru Dakshinamurti,

996
02:31:23,840 --> 02:31:26,720
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

997
02:31:26,920 --> 02:31:29,960
whose manifestations are the five elements,

998
02:31:30,160 --> 02:31:33,160
the sun, the moon and the spirit

999
02:31:33,360 --> 02:31:35,920
and whose presence is felt everywhere

1000
02:31:36,120 --> 02:31:39,360
in the universe by enlightened souls.

1001
