02:31:44,680 --> 02:31:47,960
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

1003
02:31:48,160 --> 02:31:52,560
the Guru and Lord of the three locas,

1004
02:31:52,760 --> 02:31:57,000
who is alert to remove the ??grids of birth and death,

1005
02:31:57,200 --> 02:31:59,360
who is seated on the ground at the basis

1006
02:31:59,560 --> 02:32:03,520
of the banyan tree, that is the tree of life

1007
02:32:03,720 --> 02:32:08,880
and is enlightening all the saints and sages.

1008
02:32:09,080 --> 02:32:11,800
The guru is silent -

1009
02:32:12,000 --> 02:32:19,360
is silent, but disciples of the guru become doubtless.

1010
02:32:19,960 --> 02:32:25,920
The guru looks young and the disciples old.

1011
02:32:26,120 --> 02:32:31,320
Salutation again and again to Sakshat Shri Guru Dakshinamurti,

1012
02:32:31,520 --> 02:32:34,480
Sakshat Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

1013
02:32:34,680 --> 02:32:41,240
who manifests herself before her devotees in ??bhandra mudra -

1014
02:32:41,440 --> 02:32:44,760
the posture conferring benevolence

1015
02:32:44,960 --> 02:32:49,360
and enlightens them with realization of their spirit,

1016
02:32:49,560 --> 02:32:51,760
pulsating through their being,

1017
02:32:51,960 --> 02:32:57,360
in all the three states of childhood, young age and old age -

1018
02:32:57,560 --> 02:33:03,000
wakefulness, dreams and deep sleep.

1019
02:33:03,200 --> 02:33:08,320
Sakshat Shri Adi Shakti Mataji,

1020
02:33:08,520 --> 02:33:14,840
Shri Nirmala Devi Namoh Namaha.

