1029
02:47:08,160 --> 02:47:11,840
So on behalf of Africa,

1030
02:47:12,040 --> 02:47:15,760
I'd like to ask our sister Al Ga'

1031
02:47:15,960 --> 02:47:19,760
to present to Shri Mataji a present

1032
02:47:19,960 --> 02:47:23,120
which symbolizes the wholesomeness of Jupiter

1033
02:47:23,320 --> 02:47:26,200
and the wholesomeness of Dharma.

1034
02:48:08,120 --> 02:48:09,920
This is a collection of miracle pictures

1035
02:48:10,120 --> 02:48:13,680
which is a gift of the Italian Sahaja yogis to everybody

1036
02:48:13,880 --> 02:48:19,520
who participated in this Puja and it will be distributed afterwards.

1037
02:50:15,800 --> 02:50:21,520
And now this is a present to commemorate this very auspicious day

1038
02:50:21,720 --> 02:50:23,680
that the Italian sahaja yogis

1039
02:50:23,880 --> 02:50:28,200
are presenting to Sir C.P. Shrivastava.

1040
02:50:33,960 --> 02:50:38,600
