1041
02:50:38,800 --> 02:50:42,240
should gather these at this end of the stage

1042
02:50:42,440 --> 02:50:45,720
and they will present the sari to Shri Mataji -

1043
02:50:45,920 --> 02:50:48,560
all the small countries, who did not have an opportunity

1044
02:50:48,760 --> 02:50:52,080
to offer sari to Shri Mataji before.

1045
02:51:04,960 --> 02:51:10,160
Also Taiwan, please, take back your sari and present it again now.

1046
02:51:10,400 --> 02:51:12,640
Taiwan.

1047
02:51:25,400 --> 02:51:30,040
Mai sunt țări care au sariuri de oferit?

1048
02:51:41,120 --> 02:51:44,600
And this from Vigevano an Italian city.

