02:53:06,000 --> 02:53:10,480
The next present is from Cameroon.

1050
02:53:55,200 --> 02:54:02,000
The next is Russia and Ukraine together.

1051
02:54:19,800 --> 02:54:24,800
Dr. Voronov is presenting the present from Russia.

1052
02:54:50,840 --> 02:54:54,640
Professor Voronov is the head of the academy of arts and sciences

1053
02:54:54,840 --> 02:54:57,760
in Saint Petersburg.

1054
02:56:08,080 --> 02:56:12,000
Greatest Woman of our planet,

1055
02:56:12,480 --> 02:56:15,480
Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi,

1056
02:56:16,440 --> 02:56:19,240
you have a good sputnik,

1057
02:56:19,680 --> 02:56:24,840
satellite in Sir Shrivastava.

1058
02:56:26,400 --> 02:56:29,800
Prominent government figura,

