02:56:43,840 --> 02:56:49,840
I am from my family and my friends,

1061
02:56:50,520 --> 02:56:56,000
with open heart and good wish -

1062
02:56:59,200 --> 02:57:02,600
one order Russia for you,

1063
02:57:03,400 --> 02:57:08,320
"Great Patriotic War".

1064
02:57:24,640 --> 02:57:26,800
It is order

1065
02:57:27,920 --> 02:57:31,320
second mundial war.

1066
02:57:39,440 --> 02:57:45,440
With pure, deep gratitude and sense from Russia

1067
02:57:45,680 --> 02:57:49,800
I give you, Sir Shrivastava

1068
02:57:50,640 --> 02:57:56,080
this order of the second mundial war,

1069
02:57:57,120 --> 02:58:02,400
